response.original_title: 1978 NSWRFL Grand Final: Manly Warringah Sea Eagles vs Cronulla Sutherland Sharks (Replay)
response.overview: The Tuesday rematch in front of 33,552 was Manly's sixth game in twenty-four days. It was the second Grand Final in a row to end up going into a mid-week replay with the 1977 Grand Final between St George and Parramatta also needing a re-match to decide the Premiers after the original game had been a 9-all draw.
